All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Animal
Common parent of all animal classes.
AnimalAbility
Describes an ability usable by an animal
AnimalTrait
Create a new animal trait, usable by Animal.addDefensiveTraits(AnimalTrait...) and Animal.addOffensiveTraits(AnimalTrait...)
AnimalType
Animal types (similar to classes).
BattleLog
Creates a log of the battle and saves it to a file for debug and analysis
DarkTrail
A class describing the "Dark Trail" environment, where you face an orc named Sargulg
Environment
Class containing common behaviour for all environments
Game
Holds the logic for each game/battle
Main
Selects an environment and starts a game, as well as other init stuff
